{"tid":1941398,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本將啟動「瑞德西韋」臨床試驗 與美合作抗疫","createTime":"2020-03-24T11:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T12:40:49.000Z","uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2676ec2487a00c7cb434547bba1e83ad8a925a6e","tid":1941398,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:38:41.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（COVID-19）疫情持續延燒，昨（23日）日本國立國際醫療研究中心（東京都新宿區）宣布，將啟動驗證「瑞德西韋」安全性和有效性的醫生主導的臨床試驗，將與美國合作推進，最快於本月內開始給患者用藥<br />\n<br />\n根據日媒《共同網》報導，研究中心表示，目前至少已將「瑞德西韋」用於9名患者，將通過臨床試驗詳細驗證是否符合標準藥物，對象為患有肺炎或呼吸狀態不好的20歲以上確診患者，未設定目標人數，將比較「用藥前」和「用藥15天後」的狀態，國際感染症中心長大曲貴夫表示「這是人類的危機，必須迅速確立標準的治療藥」。<br />\n<br />\n「瑞德西韋」原用於治療伊波拉病毒之研究，之後在武漢肺炎的實驗中取得了效果，被認為可能是有效的治療藥物，目前中國和美國已展開臨床試驗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3110353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3110353&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJx5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=26d29f3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3110353&h=6e4f185f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3110353</a>"},{"pid":"43832c5ba0746c3bd7f5c8c6b7e5ef41178add75","tid":1941398,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:39:33.000Z","msg":"之前唔係貪啲支人錢貪得唔舍得封支人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5efe366852a0cb03a1596e8566d8b40079d8ed","tid":1941398,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:42:50.000Z","msg":"taiwan no.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511fea5e4974afd9f73b43e4c73499f7478b8915","tid":1941398,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:51:38.000Z","msg":"台灣美國日本"},{"pi